{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04050/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04050"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:40:50"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man sits on the ground, smiling up at a model."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04050","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04050"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1/13e70ddc-ee7c-4fec-a44b-9c0592185925","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:52:56.657Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In his dialogue (heard but not seen delivered), Reynolds resists sitting on the floor. He would, of course, feel too proud to do so, but on a symbolic level, Alma standing over him as he gazes up at her reflects the change in their relationship by which she takes control. He’ll find himself on the ground, as it were, when she poisons him. A photograph of Cristóbal Balenciaga and one of his models in similar poses can be seen at the beginning of Mary Blume’s biography of the Spanish fashion designer (Blume, <em>Master of Us All</em>, 2). Notably, in that image Balenciaga kneels while the model reclines, leaving the former looking down on the latter and maintaining traditional power dynamics.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04050/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1073.7012113055182,118.14266487214005,674.4549125168237,555.5854643337819"}}}]}]}]}